# Agents: Specialized Claude Instances

## Agent Inventory

| Agent Name | Description | Model | Cost Tier | Tools | When to Use | When NOT to Use |
|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|
| **code-reviewer** | Read-only code quality, security validation, and review | Sonnet | 1x | Read, Grep, Glob | Before committing risky changes, security audit | Real-time pair programming, active implementation |
| **research-assistant** | Technical research, API exploration, decision support | Haiku | 0.4x | WebSearch, WebFetch, Read, Glob | Need to research new library or API design decision | Have full domain knowledge already, need deep reasoning |
| **architecture-reviewer** | Module design, dependency boundaries, architectural patterns | Sonnet | 1x | Read, Grep, Glob | Design review, circular dependency check, large refactoring | Line-level code review (use code-reviewer), single function review |

---

## Decision Matrix: When to Use Which Agent?

| Task Type | code-reviewer | architecture-reviewer | research-assistant | Main Session |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| **Code Review** | ✅ YES | ❌ No | ❌ No | Maybe (simple changes) |
| **Security Audit** | ✅ YES | ❌ No | ❌ No | No |
| **API Research** | ❌ No | ❌ No | ✅ YES | Maybe (familiar API) |
| **Library Comparison** | ❌ No | ❌ No | ✅ YES | Maybe (need reasoning) |
| **Implementation** | ❌ No | ❌ No | ❌ No | ✅ YES |
| **Architecture Design** | ❌ No | ✅ YES | Maybe | ✅ YES |
| **Module Boundaries** | ❌ No | ✅ YES | ❌ No | Maybe |

---

## Invocation Guide

```
@code-reviewer: Review the authentication logic in src/auth.ts for security issues
```
```
@research-assistant: What are the trade-offs between React Query and SWR for data fetching?
```
```
@architecture-reviewer: Review the module structure in src/ — ada circular dependency?
```

